  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 27-33-75, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO ALLOW AN EXEMPTION FROM ALL AD VALOREM TAXES ON THE ASSESSED VALUE OF THE HOMESTEAD PROPERTY FOR A QUALIFIED HOMEOWNER WHO IS AN AMERICAN VETERAN WHO HAS BEEN HONORABLY DISCHARGED FROM MILITARY SERVICE, FOR A QUALIFIED HOMEOWNER WHO HAS REACHED 65 YEARS OF AGE AND HIS OR HER UNREMARRIED SURVIVING SPOUSE, AND FOR AN ACTIVE-DUTY MEMBER OF THE UNITED STATES ARMED FORCES; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
  },
